  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata-grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the seafood mix onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Brush the rendered fat onto the seafood, then season with salt, black pepper, and garlic powder.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until cooked through.",
    "Remove the kebabs from the grill and brush with lemon juice.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve immediately."
